com.qualcomm.robotcore.hardware.configuration.annotations

Annotation Type ExpansionHubPIDFVelocityParams


  • @Documented
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ExpansionHubPIDFVelocityParams
    When ExpansionHubPIDFVelocityParams annotations are placed on a motor type, the indicated PIDF coefficients are automatically initialized when instances of that motor are used.
